SBM                     Main function of the Stochastic Block Model
                        (SBM)
convertSBtoNormal       Convert the vector v into the vector theta/phi
                        using the stick-breaking formula
get.logl                Calculate the log-likelihood
getql                   Summarize data for SBM according to the
                        different location and species groups
gibbs.SAM               Main function of the Species Archetype Model
                        (SAM)
mixture.gibbs.main.func
                        Main function of the Mixture Model
ncs                     Summarize the data for mixture model
sample.alpha            Sample alpha
sample.betas            Sample betas
sample.cs               Sample cs
sample.gamma            Sample the TSB prior parameter
sample.gamma.sam        Sample gamma
sample.gamma.u          Sample gamma.u
sample.gamma.v          Sample gamma.v
sample.omega            Sample omega
sample.phi              Sample phi and uk parameters
sample.psi              Sample psi parameters
sample.theta            Sample theta and vk parameters
sample.theta.sam        Sample theta
sample.w                Sample w
sample.z                Sample z
tnorm                   Sample from a truncated normal distribution
update.theta            Samples theta and v parameters
update.z                Samples z
